We need to show `D ≤ @DirectSumDecomposition.refinement C inst✝¹ K inst✝ M D B hB hB' hB''`.
This is equivalent to showing `IsRefinement (@DirectSumDecomposition.refinement C inst✝¹ K inst✝ M D B hB hB' hB'') D`.

